emulib.emustudio.debugtable

Interface DebugTable


  • public interface DebugTable
    This interface allows updating Debug table in emuStudio by any plug-in.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void refresh()
      Redraws debug table according to actual values.
      void setCustomColumns(List<DebugColumn> customColumns)
      Set custom columns in debugger.
      void setDefaultColumns()
      Set default columns in debugger.

    • Method Detail

      • refresh

        void refresh()
        Redraws debug table according to actual values.

      • setCustomColumns

        void setCustomColumns(List<DebugColumn> customColumns)
        Set custom columns in debugger.
        Parameters:
        customColumns - non-null debug columns
        See Also:
        AddressColumn, BreakpointColumn, MnemoColumn, OpcodeColumn

      • setDefaultColumns

        void setDefaultColumns()
        Set default columns in debugger. Default columns is specific for emuStudio. Usually, there is breakpoint column, address, mnemo and opcode.
